theme-prefs-label: Label of the theme settings shown on Special:Preferences, in the appearance tab
theme-livepreview-note: Note shown on Special:Preferences, in the appearance tab, when previewing a theme. $1 is the name of a theme, e.g. dark, stellarbook etc.
theme-unsupported-skin: Note shown on Special:Preferences, in the appearance tab, instead of the theme selector if the user is using a skin which does not support themes.
theme-name-monobook-stellarbook:
{{optional}}
Name of the StellarBook theme for the MonoBook skin
